<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Renewal Reminder - Fifty Firsts Wellness</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5aa0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .renewal-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #2c5aa0;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .renewal-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5aa0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .renewal-details {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .renewal-details li {
            padding: 5px 0;
            color: #666;
        }
        .renewal-details li:before {
            content: "• ";
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .benefits-box {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .benefits-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .benefits-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .benefits-list li {
            padding: 5px 0;
            color: #666;
        }
        .benefits-list li:before {
            content: "• ";
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2c5aa0;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Fifty Firsts Wellness</div>
            <div class="subtitle">Subscription Renewal Reminder</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Dear <%= firstName || 'Valued Member' %>,</h2>
            
            <p>Your Fifty Firsts Wellness subscription is up for renewal!</p>

            <div class="renewal-box">
                <div class="renewal-title">Renewal Details:</div>
                <ul class="renewal-details">
                    <li>Current subscription: <%= subscriptionType || 'Check your account for details' %></li>
                    <li>Renewal date: <%= renewalDate || 'Check your account for the date' %></li>
                    <li>Benefits: Continue accessing all premium features and content</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="benefits-box">
                <div class="benefits-title">Why Renew:</div>
                <ul class="benefits-list">
                    <li>Maintain access to all wellness programs</li>
                    <li>Keep your progress tracking active</li>
                    <li>Continue receiving expert guidance</li>
                    <li>Stay connected with our community</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>Don't let your wellness journey pause - renew today and keep moving forward!</p>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= renewalLink || 'https://fiftyfirstswellness.com/renew' %>" class="cta-button">
                    Renew Now
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Best regards,</strong><br>
            The Fifty Firsts Wellness Team</p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p><strong>Questions about your subscription?</strong><br>
                Contact us at <%= companyEmail || 'support@fiftyfirstswellness.com' %></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
